
## ðŸ”¨ How the Lambda Function Works

- Triggered on `PUT` events from S3 Bucket A
- Resizes uploaded image to 300x300 pixels
- Stores result in S3 Bucket B with prefix `resized-`

## ðŸ“¦ Lambda Layer Notes

Pillow was installed on an Amazon Linux 2023 EC2 instance to ensure compatibility with Lambda Python 3.12 runtime.

```bash
mkdir -p python/lib/python3.12/site-packages
python3.12 -m pip install pillow -t python/lib/python3.12/site-packages/
zip -r9 pillow-layer-python312.zip python
